WEBVTT

00:00:02.900 --> 00:00:04.400
Chief Justice Lu, I'm sorry.

00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:05.800
You had to come out
even though you're busy.

00:00:05.933 --> 00:00:06.933
I am really busy.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:08.200
Councilor Huang.

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:09.433
Keep it short.

00:00:09.833 --> 00:00:10.833
Chief Justice Lu.

00:00:11.033 --> 00:00:12.733
I've been hearing
a lot of news lately.

00:00:13.333 --> 00:00:14.733
Public opinion also supports...

00:00:14.733 --> 00:00:16.000
our development
of the Old City District.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:17.333
So you want to support...

00:00:17.733 --> 00:00:20.366
your friends
who are in real estate, right?

00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:23.133
We just want to promote...

00:00:23.133 --> 00:00:24.600
Hokong's economic development.

00:00:25.633 --> 00:00:26.666
With your intelligence,

00:00:27.266 --> 00:00:28.666
don't you think you can come up...

00:00:28.666 --> 00:00:29.966
with a perfect solution?

00:00:29.966 --> 00:00:31.633
I'll have to see if it's necessary.

00:00:32.266 --> 00:00:33.333
As Chief Justice,

00:00:34.033 --> 00:00:35.566
many people are watching me.

00:00:36.433 --> 00:00:37.800
I have to set an example.

00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:39.166
I can't set a bad one, right?

00:00:40.933 --> 00:00:42.066
Judge Lu, have some coffee.

00:00:43.033 --> 00:00:44.166
I'm really busy.

00:00:44.166 --> 00:00:45.533
Let's talk next time.

00:03:12.600 --> 00:03:16.300
(Justice is Mine)

00:03:16.933 --> 00:03:19.333
(Episode 16)

00:03:22.600 --> 00:03:23.600
The doctor said...

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:24.866
even after discharge,

00:03:24.866 --> 00:03:26.600
you have to finish
your anti-inflammatory medicine.

00:03:27.466 --> 00:03:28.466
Okay.

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:31.433
Does Yi Wei know
I'll be visiting him?

00:03:31.433 --> 00:03:33.000
I've already told him.

00:03:34.066 --> 00:03:35.433
I'll go and get the car.

00:03:35.500 --> 00:03:36.500
Then you don't have to
walk that far.

00:03:36.500 --> 00:03:37.500
Okay.

00:03:37.733 --> 00:03:38.833
I'll call you
when I get to the entrance.

00:03:38.833 --> 00:03:39.833
Okay, thank you.

00:03:47.033 --> 00:03:48.033
Let's talk.

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:49.633
Are you here to rob me again?

00:03:50.033 --> 00:03:51.733
If you approve
my dad's medical parole,

00:03:52.633 --> 00:03:53.866
then it won't happen again.

00:03:55.233 --> 00:03:56.466
You've got some nerve.

00:03:56.933 --> 00:03:58.333
You failed to kill me.

00:03:58.633 --> 00:03:59.766
Now, you want me to work for you.

00:04:01.233 --> 00:04:02.733
My dad has a weak heart.

00:04:03.966 --> 00:04:06.933
Plus, my elder brother's murder
was a huge blow to him.

00:04:06.933 --> 00:04:08.666
If something happens
to him in prison,

00:04:09.466 --> 00:04:10.966
do you think it might
have something to do with you?

00:04:13.166 --> 00:04:14.600
I've prepared all the documents.

00:04:15.766 --> 00:04:16.766
Sign this.

00:04:18.600 --> 00:04:20.933
Han Kui Long's release
on medical parole...

00:04:21.066 --> 00:04:22.066
would require the approval...

00:04:22.266 --> 00:04:23.766
of the Chief Justice, Judge Lu.

00:04:24.933 --> 00:04:25.933
Lu Wei De?

00:04:28.266 --> 00:04:29.600
What? Haven't you seen the news?

00:04:33.366 --> 00:04:34.833
Let's talk
after you've watched the news.

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:40.800
Right.

00:04:41.533 --> 00:04:43.033
There's something
I didn't tell you yet.

00:04:43.566 --> 00:04:44.566
From now on,

00:04:45.533 --> 00:04:46.533
I'm in charge of the Han family.

00:04:55.566 --> 00:04:58.466
Last night, on the curved slope
of Changyun Road...

00:04:58.766 --> 00:05:00.166
in the Western District,
which is an accident blackspot,

00:05:00.166 --> 00:05:01.533
a serious car accident occurred.

00:05:01.933 --> 00:05:03.033
After the driver was extracted
from the car,

00:05:03.033 --> 00:05:04.033
he was pronounced dead.

00:05:04.033 --> 00:05:05.033
It has been confirmed...

00:05:05.233 --> 00:05:06.600
that the deceased...

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:08.066
is the newly appointed
Chief Justice, Lu Wei De.

00:05:08.566 --> 00:05:09.966
The police's initial speculation...

00:05:09.966 --> 00:05:12.233
is that the accident was caused
by human error.

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.866
For more information,

00:05:13.866 --> 00:05:15.566
please tune in to the midday news.

00:05:16.633 --> 00:05:17.766
We'll go to a commercial break now.

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:21.800
Judge Qin.

00:05:22.166 --> 00:05:23.266
Excuse me, I'm rushing to a meeting.

00:05:23.533 --> 00:05:25.533
What happened to Chief Justice Lu
is truly a shame.

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:28.800
Indeed.

00:05:29.466 --> 00:05:31.266
Chief Justice Lu
was a very cautious man.

00:05:31.733 --> 00:05:33.666
This car accident
happening to him...

00:05:34.533 --> 00:05:35.566
is truly quite unexpected.

00:05:36.733 --> 00:05:37.833
Being cautious is good,

00:05:38.133 --> 00:05:39.133
but being too cautious...

00:05:39.266 --> 00:05:40.633
can make you
lose judgment in a crisis.

00:05:41.466 --> 00:05:42.466
I'm really busy.

00:05:42.666 --> 00:05:43.966
Let's talk next time.

00:05:48.200 --> 00:05:49.200
Councilor Huang.

00:05:49.466 --> 00:05:50.466
It's all right.

00:05:50.966 --> 00:05:52.033
If he doesn't want this coffee,

00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:53.833
I'll let someone else have it.

00:06:01.400 --> 00:06:02.400
By the way, Judge Qin,

00:06:02.733 --> 00:06:03.733
have you heard...

00:06:03.733 --> 00:06:05.200
about the Old City District
land deed case...

00:06:05.200 --> 00:06:06.266
that Chief Justice Lu was handling?

00:06:09.066 --> 00:06:10.166
Given my rank,

00:06:10.533 --> 00:06:12.433
I don't have access to cases
handled by the Chief Justice.

00:06:13.133 --> 00:06:14.333
Given your qualifications,

00:06:14.566 --> 00:06:16.600
you're very likely to take over
his position.

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:17.833
My abilities are limited.

00:06:17.833 --> 00:06:19.966
Otherwise,
I wouldn't have lost to Judge Lu.

00:06:20.566 --> 00:06:21.733
As for the land deed case,

00:06:21.733 --> 00:06:23.200
it's not my area of expertise.

00:06:23.566 --> 00:06:24.933
It'll be hard for me
to make a decision...

00:06:24.933 --> 00:06:25.966
that satisfies all parties.

00:06:26.266 --> 00:06:27.266
That's not true.

00:06:27.533 --> 00:06:28.833
You handled Shi Zhi Yang's case...

00:06:28.833 --> 00:06:30.200
very well.

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:32.333
I think you'll be able
to handle cases...

00:06:32.633 --> 00:06:34.233
that have a social impact.

00:06:34.566 --> 00:06:35.566
The appointment of Chief Justice...

00:06:35.566 --> 00:06:37.233
requires promulgation
from the administrative body.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:39.000
Judge Qin.

00:06:39.366 --> 00:06:42.233
I think you are definitely
the most desirable candidate.

00:06:42.566 --> 00:06:43.600
All you have to do...

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:45.266
is take over
the Chief Justice position.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.666
Just like the development
of the Old City District,

00:06:47.666 --> 00:06:48.666
it's inevitable.

00:06:48.933 --> 00:06:49.933
That's where the wind is blowing.

00:06:51.966 --> 00:06:53.400
Councilor Huang, excuse me.

00:06:53.533 --> 00:06:55.166
Judge Qin, everyone's here.
It's time for the meeting.

00:06:55.666 --> 00:06:56.933
I'll leave you to it, Judge Qin.

00:06:57.166 --> 00:06:58.533
I hope to hear good news...

00:06:58.533 --> 00:07:00.200
about your promotion soon.

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:05.733
In order not to affect the trial,

00:07:06.533 --> 00:07:07.933
Chief Justice Lu's cases...

00:07:08.466 --> 00:07:09.933
will be taken over
by you, Judge Qin.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:12.033
As for the Chief Justice's
certificate of appointment,

00:07:12.933 --> 00:07:14.066
it will be announced soon.

00:07:14.066 --> 00:07:16.133
I'm sorry.
I want to think about it first.

00:07:16.233 --> 00:07:17.533
There's no need to think about it.

00:07:17.766 --> 00:07:19.666
If you hadn't withdrawn
so early last time,

00:07:19.933 --> 00:07:22.066
the Chief Justice position
would've been yours.

00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:24.666
I think you truly deserve it.

00:07:24.866 --> 00:07:26.066
I still want to think about it.

00:07:59.833 --> 00:08:02.266
An inmate riot broke out
at midnight at the Hokong Prison.

00:08:02.266 --> 00:08:03.466
The situation is extremely chaotic.

00:08:03.633 --> 00:08:05.366
Armed police have been dispatched...

00:08:05.366 --> 00:08:06.733
to deal with the situation.

00:08:16.066 --> 00:08:17.066
This is an emergency.

00:08:17.066 --> 00:08:18.233
No one can go in.

00:08:18.566 --> 00:08:19.600
No, my son is in there.

00:08:19.600 --> 00:08:20.600
I'm sorry, Judge Qin.

00:08:20.633 --> 00:08:21.633
We have orders from up top.

00:08:21.633 --> 00:08:22.633
No one can go in.

00:08:22.866 --> 00:08:23.866
Judge Qin.

00:08:24.166 --> 00:08:25.166
The Riot Squad has gone in.

00:08:25.333 --> 00:08:26.366
The riot has been quelled.

00:08:26.866 --> 00:08:27.966
Some inmates were injured.

00:08:27.966 --> 00:08:29.266
We don't know how your son is yet.

00:08:30.366 --> 00:08:31.366
I want to see my son.

00:08:31.933 --> 00:08:33.400
I'll go in and talk to the warden.

00:08:33.433 --> 00:08:34.433
Don't worry.

00:08:34.433 --> 00:08:36.433
I take your matters seriously.

00:08:36.800 --> 00:08:38.066
Mr. Feng, wait to hear from me.

00:08:39.166 --> 00:08:40.166
Councilor Huang.

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:42.200
I want to see the warden.

00:08:42.466 --> 00:08:44.233
Councilor Huang is
on the Supervision Committee...

00:08:44.400 --> 00:08:45.866
of the Correctional Services
Department.

00:08:45.866 --> 00:08:47.033
You have no right to stop him.

00:08:47.033 --> 00:08:48.033
Hurry up!

00:08:50.133 --> 00:08:51.133
Please come with me.

00:08:57.933 --> 00:09:00.066
Councilor Huang, you came
all this way so late.

00:09:01.100 --> 00:09:02.100
This is a serious matter.

00:09:02.100 --> 00:09:03.266
Of course, I had to come right away.

00:09:03.666 --> 00:09:04.866
I'm on the Supervision Committee.

00:09:05.166 --> 00:09:06.633
Supervision is my responsibility.

00:09:07.466 --> 00:09:09.466
It's those gangsters
who were causing trouble.

00:09:09.866 --> 00:09:10.866
I took care of it.

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.833
I'll keep a closer eye
on them in the future.

00:09:12.833 --> 00:09:14.433
I have faith in you.

00:09:15.333 --> 00:09:16.566
But the Chief Justice...

00:09:16.566 --> 00:09:17.733
is not too pleased.

00:09:18.466 --> 00:09:19.766
Why is he not pleased?

00:09:20.166 --> 00:09:21.400
I can explain it to him.

00:09:22.433 --> 00:09:23.966
Explain it to him?

00:09:24.266 --> 00:09:25.400
It's better to let him see
with his own eyes...

00:09:25.400 --> 00:09:26.433
that his son is fine.

00:09:26.600 --> 00:09:27.800
It's more convincing that way.

00:09:28.866 --> 00:09:29.866
His son?

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:31.000
Qin Yi Wei.

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:33.766
Isn't his dad a judge?

00:09:34.033 --> 00:09:35.033
He's a judge.

00:09:35.533 --> 00:09:36.533
But very soon,

00:09:36.833 --> 00:09:38.833
he'll be the new Chief Justice.

00:09:48.166 --> 00:09:49.166
- Dad.
- Yi Wei.

00:09:49.333 --> 00:09:50.333
Are you okay?

00:09:50.566 --> 00:09:51.566
You're hurt.

00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:52.800
You're bleeding so much.

00:09:53.166 --> 00:09:54.166
It's not my blood.

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:55.600
I'm fine.

00:10:05.800 --> 00:10:06.800
Hey.

00:10:06.866 --> 00:10:07.866
Are you okay?

00:10:09.433 --> 00:10:10.433
Can you hang in there?

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:17.600
Is this how you ensure
the safety of the prisoners?

00:10:17.966 --> 00:10:19.533
I promise to tighten security
from now on.

00:10:21.166 --> 00:10:22.166
Sir.

00:10:22.166 --> 00:10:23.166
I have a suggestion,

00:10:23.166 --> 00:10:24.166
but I'm not sure
if it's appropriate.

00:10:24.733 --> 00:10:25.933
Take Qin Yi Wei, for example.

00:10:26.066 --> 00:10:27.733
He's a young man who's willing
to turn over a new leaf.

00:10:28.333 --> 00:10:29.733
He shouldn't be locked up
with the general population.

00:10:30.666 --> 00:10:31.833
There are too many bad people
among the inmates.

00:10:32.033 --> 00:10:33.133
He could easily go astray.

00:10:34.166 --> 00:10:36.200
Is there any chance of him
transferring to a four-person cell?

00:10:36.533 --> 00:10:38.166
The disciplinary rules
there are lighter,

00:10:38.166 --> 00:10:39.166
and the inmates
are about the same age.

00:10:39.766 --> 00:10:40.766
Most importantly,

00:10:40.933 --> 00:10:42.400
Judge Qin won't have to worry.

00:10:44.166 --> 00:10:45.166
That's a good idea.

00:10:45.400 --> 00:10:46.766
Let's go with that.

00:10:55.800 --> 00:10:57.266
Everything is finally settled.

00:10:57.866 --> 00:10:58.866
That's why I say...

00:10:58.933 --> 00:11:00.633
there's no problem
that can't be solved.

00:11:01.400 --> 00:11:02.466
Thank you for your help...

00:11:02.966 --> 00:11:04.033
with Yi Wei this time,
Councilor Huang.

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.000
Judge Qin,

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:08.000
I heard the Chief Justice's
certificate of appointment...

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:09.000
is coming soon.

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:10.966
Should I congratulate you
in advance?

00:11:12.066 --> 00:11:13.266
Can we talk about it later?

00:11:13.733 --> 00:11:14.866
I just got out of the hospital,

00:11:15.366 --> 00:11:16.733
and I'm not feeling well.

00:11:17.800 --> 00:11:19.833
Well, Judge Qin, you must take care.

00:11:20.166 --> 00:11:21.566
Most importantly, stay healthy.

00:11:21.966 --> 00:11:23.266
You still have to take care
of your son.

00:11:26.566 --> 00:11:27.566
Okay.

00:11:55.033 --> 00:11:56.033
What's wrong?

00:11:58.233 --> 00:11:59.766
It's fine. He's our new friend.

00:11:59.766 --> 00:12:00.766
We'll take good care of him.

00:12:14.633 --> 00:12:15.833
You sleep on this bed.

00:12:16.666 --> 00:12:17.733
There's a lot of sunlight,

00:12:17.833 --> 00:12:18.866
and the air is fresh.

00:12:21.766 --> 00:12:22.766
Come.

00:12:23.666 --> 00:12:24.666
Come here.

00:12:25.066 --> 00:12:26.066
Sit down.

00:12:27.666 --> 00:12:28.800
Do I have to invite you to sit?

00:12:30.033 --> 00:12:31.033
Sit down.

00:12:35.233 --> 00:12:36.666
Mr. Lie told us...

00:12:36.866 --> 00:12:38.400
to take good care of you.

00:12:40.066 --> 00:12:41.966
Don't make your dad worry.

00:12:51.200 --> 00:12:52.466
He's still new here.

00:12:52.466 --> 00:12:53.766
Go easy on him.

00:12:54.166 --> 00:12:55.866
- Right?
- You're dead if anything happens.

00:13:12.633 --> 00:13:14.266
Congratulations, Chief Justice Qin.

00:13:15.633 --> 00:13:16.633
Is it worth it?

00:13:17.833 --> 00:13:19.666
The first day you put on
this judicial robe,

00:13:19.966 --> 00:13:21.433
you set a goal for yourself.

00:13:24.666 --> 00:13:25.733
Do I deserve it?

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:32.766
You hoped to use the power...

00:13:32.766 --> 00:13:34.000
granted to you as Chief Justice...

00:13:34.366 --> 00:13:36.400
to uphold the rule of law
and justice.

00:13:40.566 --> 00:13:41.800
You're a good father.

00:13:42.566 --> 00:13:43.566
I believe...

00:13:43.800 --> 00:13:45.666
you can still stay true
to your original intention.

00:13:46.866 --> 00:13:47.933
Can I really?

00:13:49.866 --> 00:13:51.800
Chief Justice, it's time for court.

00:13:57.233 --> 00:13:59.066
- What?
- We need to get ready for court.

00:14:01.366 --> 00:14:02.366
Okay.

00:14:04.933 --> 00:14:05.933
Your Honor.

00:14:06.133 --> 00:14:07.966
According to the prosecution,
this land deed...

00:14:07.966 --> 00:14:09.966
was issued by the interim government
100 years ago.

00:14:10.866 --> 00:14:11.866
It is permanently valid.

00:14:13.866 --> 00:14:14.866
Your Honor.

00:14:15.266 --> 00:14:17.033
First, that is a fact.

00:14:17.133 --> 00:14:18.133
Second,

00:14:18.233 --> 00:14:19.233
the deed stipulates...

00:14:19.366 --> 00:14:21.466
that all land resolutions
in the Old City District...

00:14:21.466 --> 00:14:22.466
must be approved...

00:14:22.666 --> 00:14:24.233
by all residents.

00:14:24.766 --> 00:14:25.800
More than half of the residents
must support the resolution...

00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:26.800
before it can be implemented.

00:14:29.666 --> 00:14:30.666
My great-grandfather...

00:14:30.700 --> 00:14:33.000
also had an appointment letter
given by the government,

00:14:33.266 --> 00:14:34.466
stating that the men
of our family...

00:14:34.466 --> 00:14:35.533
could inherit the position...

00:14:35.533 --> 00:14:37.166
of Minister of Justice
for generations.

00:14:38.033 --> 00:14:39.033
But then,

00:14:39.233 --> 00:14:40.233
to this day,

00:14:40.666 --> 00:14:42.266
what can a tattered piece
of paper...

00:14:42.666 --> 00:14:44.066
really represent?

00:14:44.966 --> 00:14:46.800
The defense counsel clearly
does not respect...

00:14:46.800 --> 00:14:48.400
the historical credentials
of the indigenous people.

00:14:49.166 --> 00:14:51.066
According to Article 145,
Chapter 2 of the Constitution,

00:14:51.066 --> 00:14:52.133
it is stipulated that...

00:14:52.766 --> 00:14:54.933
any archives, documents, or deeds...

00:14:54.933 --> 00:14:56.833
obtained under the original law,

00:14:56.833 --> 00:14:59.466
and the rights
and obligations they contain...

00:14:59.766 --> 00:15:01.566
shall remain valid,

00:15:01.566 --> 00:15:02.566
provided they do not
contradict the current law.

00:15:02.800 --> 00:15:05.766
They are recognized and protected
by the current government.

00:15:06.733 --> 00:15:08.033
I'm not questioning
the Constitution.

00:15:08.200 --> 00:15:10.666
But someone is exploiting
the legitimacy of this land deed.

00:15:10.866 --> 00:15:11.866
Everyone knows...

00:15:11.866 --> 00:15:13.433
that the Old City District
has a high crime rate.

00:15:13.433 --> 00:15:14.566
It's overrun by gangs.

00:15:14.866 --> 00:15:16.766
Can the residents
really vote fairly?

00:15:17.266 --> 00:15:18.266
Or are they...

00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:19.933
controlled by a bunch of people...

00:15:19.933 --> 00:15:20.933
with criminal records?

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:22.433
- What did you say?
- What are you saying?

00:15:22.433 --> 00:15:23.533
I dare you to say it again.

00:15:23.866 --> 00:15:25.200
I'll give you a chance
to say it again.

