00:29:11.266 --> 00:29:12.266
Yes.

00:29:12.666 --> 00:29:13.666
It's a little better.

00:29:14.966 --> 00:29:15.966
That's good.

00:29:18.266 --> 00:29:19.866
It's been getting cold lately.

00:29:19.866 --> 00:29:20.933
Do you have enough clothes?

00:29:23.666 --> 00:29:25.600
I heard that Judge Qin...

00:29:25.600 --> 00:29:26.833
is very stubborn.

00:29:27.633 --> 00:29:29.066
How did you take care of him?

00:29:30.966 --> 00:29:31.966
Five words.

00:29:32.766 --> 00:29:34.133
To each their own need.

00:29:34.766 --> 00:29:35.833
There's nothing we can't handle.

00:29:37.400 --> 00:29:39.266
What about...

00:29:39.933 --> 00:29:41.033
the deed in court?

00:29:42.200 --> 00:29:43.266
It's also five words.

00:29:43.433 --> 00:29:44.933
Let fate take its course.

00:29:44.933 --> 00:29:46.200
It all worked out naturally.

00:29:51.166 --> 00:29:53.533
No matter how I look at it,

00:29:54.666 --> 00:29:56.066
this deed couldn't possibly be fake.

00:29:57.000 --> 00:29:58.000
Impossible.

00:29:59.200 --> 00:30:00.200
Granduncle.

00:30:00.633 --> 00:30:01.633
Don't be like this.

00:30:02.033 --> 00:30:03.033
Just...

00:30:03.700 --> 00:30:05.066
put away this deed.

00:30:05.966 --> 00:30:07.866
The judge has already ruled it fake.

00:30:08.033 --> 00:30:09.866
It's as good as scrap paper.

00:30:09.866 --> 00:30:11.333
It doesn't matter
if we keep it or not.

00:30:11.866 --> 00:30:13.166
That's true.

00:30:13.600 --> 00:30:14.966
But since you're our chairman,

00:30:15.166 --> 00:30:16.600
we'll have to trouble you
to gather our villagers...

00:30:16.766 --> 00:30:18.566
and try to negotiate
a good price.

00:30:18.566 --> 00:30:20.133
That's all we can do now.

00:30:20.666 --> 00:30:22.633
But I also need
you and Chang Rong...

00:30:23.166 --> 00:30:24.933
to talk to the people
of the Old City District first.

00:30:24.933 --> 00:30:25.933
No problem.

00:30:26.466 --> 00:30:28.766
Our fellow villagers' business
is our business too.

00:30:28.766 --> 00:30:30.833
We will go through fire and water
for them till the very end.

00:30:31.233 --> 00:30:32.233
Thank you.

00:30:33.166 --> 00:30:34.166
Everyone.

00:30:34.400 --> 00:30:35.566
The court's decision...

00:30:35.566 --> 00:30:36.600
is in my hands.

00:30:37.066 --> 00:30:39.233
The land acquisition project
can be fully launched.

00:30:39.766 --> 00:30:41.466
I'd like to propose another toast.

00:30:41.666 --> 00:30:42.666
Here's to the success...

00:30:42.800 --> 00:30:45.566
of the Old City District
Development Project.

00:30:46.066 --> 00:30:47.200
Let's work together...

00:30:47.633 --> 00:30:48.633
and share the success.

00:30:49.033 --> 00:30:50.033
Cheers!

00:30:58.033 --> 00:30:59.433
I have two friends who are here.

00:30:59.433 --> 00:31:00.466
I'm going to say hello.

00:31:00.966 --> 00:31:01.966
Enjoy the meal.

00:31:09.400 --> 00:31:10.866
Hello, sorry to keep you waiting.

00:31:12.433 --> 00:31:13.433
I'm going to the restroom.

00:31:16.333 --> 00:31:18.033
They wouldn't let me leave
until I had two drinks.

00:31:18.033 --> 00:31:19.033
Goodness.

00:31:20.400 --> 00:31:21.633
Don't give me that.

00:31:21.633 --> 00:31:22.633
Just drink and eat.

00:31:22.633 --> 00:31:23.766
It's not like I was waiting for you.

00:31:24.333 --> 00:31:25.333
Hey, Officer Da.

00:31:25.600 --> 00:31:26.733
I really must toast you.

00:31:27.333 --> 00:31:29.266
If you hadn't swapped the deeds
this time,

00:31:29.466 --> 00:31:30.866
we might not have made it through.

00:31:31.466 --> 00:31:33.000
If Qin Yu hadn't reminded me,

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:34.133
I would've really forgotten.

00:31:35.200 --> 00:31:36.800
During the forged documents
case last year,

00:31:37.433 --> 00:31:38.800
a whole set of tools
was confiscated...

00:31:38.800 --> 00:31:39.833
and stored in the evidence room.

00:31:40.566 --> 00:31:41.833
That set of tools is very useful.

00:31:42.166 --> 00:31:44.000
No matter
if it's a government document...

00:31:44.000 --> 00:31:45.233
or a medal,

00:31:45.466 --> 00:31:46.866
it can be made to look real.

00:31:47.200 --> 00:31:48.733
Even experts
can't tell the difference.

00:31:49.533 --> 00:31:51.666
That case was handled by Judge Qin.

00:31:51.666 --> 00:31:53.000
Of course, he remembers it clearly.

00:31:55.666 --> 00:31:58.566
Smart people are truly quick-witted.

00:31:58.833 --> 00:31:59.833
Then let's raise a glass...

00:32:00.366 --> 00:32:02.000
to our eye for good people.

00:32:02.266 --> 00:32:03.266
Come on.

00:32:03.266 --> 00:32:04.266
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

00:32:11.400 --> 00:32:13.066
If you can't touch Judge Qin,

00:32:14.233 --> 00:32:15.233
I wonder if you'll suffer
from kidney failure...

00:32:15.233 --> 00:32:16.233
from holding it in.

00:32:16.566 --> 00:32:17.566
It's none of your business.

00:32:18.033 --> 00:32:19.066
How is it not my business?

00:32:20.266 --> 00:32:22.366
I still have to return
this bullet to him.

00:32:25.266 --> 00:32:26.433
His life is mine.

00:32:27.200 --> 00:32:28.200
I have my own plans...

00:32:28.800 --> 00:32:29.800
for when to make a move on him.

00:32:32.166 --> 00:32:33.166
Fine.

00:32:33.366 --> 00:32:34.366
I won't fight with you.

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:36.000
Even if I don't get
to take his life,

00:32:36.433 --> 00:32:37.633
I'll have to collect some interest.

00:32:38.166 --> 00:32:39.166
Do you need help?

00:32:46.233 --> 00:32:47.233
Mr. Huang.

00:32:47.266 --> 00:32:48.566
Qi Chang Rong wants to use...

00:32:48.566 --> 00:32:49.833
the public's anger
in the land case...

00:32:49.833 --> 00:32:50.833
against Judge Qin.

00:32:52.266 --> 00:32:53.266
It's okay.

00:32:53.766 --> 00:32:55.233
Making them
look like unruly citizens...

00:32:55.233 --> 00:32:56.366
is good for our land acquisition.

00:32:56.966 --> 00:32:58.000
But don't go too far.

00:32:58.466 --> 00:33:00.166
Qin Yu is still useful to us.

00:33:00.466 --> 00:33:01.800
People never change.

00:33:02.766 --> 00:33:04.066
I don't believe those two...

00:33:04.466 --> 00:33:05.766
can restrain themselves
from causing trouble.

00:33:05.966 --> 00:33:07.333
Triads...

00:33:07.633 --> 00:33:08.633
can only be used as a tool.

00:33:08.633 --> 00:33:09.666
They can't be trusted.

00:33:10.266 --> 00:33:12.066
If we want peace and prosperity,

00:33:12.800 --> 00:33:14.600
we have to rely on you, Officer Da.

00:33:16.233 --> 00:33:17.266
Come on, cheers!

00:33:21.566 --> 00:33:22.566
You corrupt official!

00:33:23.766 --> 00:33:24.866
You're colluding with businessmen!

00:33:25.400 --> 00:33:26.400
Come out!

00:33:26.866 --> 00:33:28.633
Come out! Come out!

00:33:28.633 --> 00:33:30.000
You corrupt official! Come out!

00:33:30.233 --> 00:33:31.466
You're colluding with businessmen!

00:33:31.466 --> 00:33:33.166
- Corrupt official!
- Corrupt official!

00:33:40.400 --> 00:33:41.400
Come out!

00:33:41.466 --> 00:33:42.833
- Come out!
- Come out!

00:33:42.833 --> 00:33:43.833
Come out!

00:33:44.833 --> 00:33:45.833
Corrupt official!

00:33:46.233 --> 00:33:47.366
You're colluding with businessmen!

00:33:48.666 --> 00:33:50.633
- Come out!
- What kind of official are you?

00:33:50.833 --> 00:33:51.833
Corrupt official!

00:33:52.233 --> 00:33:53.233
Get out here!

00:33:55.066 --> 00:33:56.066
Come out!

00:33:57.800 --> 00:33:59.400
- Come out!
- Come out!

00:34:00.066 --> 00:34:01.066
Let's go.

00:34:21.433 --> 00:34:22.433
Madam.

00:34:27.000 --> 00:34:28.000
Where's Judge Qin?

00:34:28.000 --> 00:34:29.833
Madam, Judge Qin
is downstairs in the study.

00:34:43.666 --> 00:34:44.766
What a surprise.

00:34:45.466 --> 00:34:47.633
I never expected that you'd be
called a corrupt official one day.

00:34:50.466 --> 00:34:51.466
I didn't deny it.

00:34:53.533 --> 00:34:54.933
I could understand it...

00:34:55.533 --> 00:34:56.733
when you were trying
to protect your son.

00:34:57.600 --> 00:34:59.333
But why did you frame Shi Zhi Yang?

00:34:59.666 --> 00:35:00.733
What did you get out of it?

00:35:01.266 --> 00:35:02.466
Did you become the Chief Justice...

00:35:02.966 --> 00:35:04.733
and colluded with Da Gama...

00:35:05.466 --> 00:35:07.066
in exchange for his protection?

00:35:09.000 --> 00:35:10.000
These...

00:35:10.466 --> 00:35:11.800
are just your speculations.

00:35:14.333 --> 00:35:15.533
I trust Shi Zhi Yang.

00:35:16.166 --> 00:35:17.166
So I believe...

00:35:17.933 --> 00:35:19.066
that your ruling on him...

00:35:20.033 --> 00:35:21.033
was wrong.

00:35:23.666 --> 00:35:24.666
Guo Hua.

00:35:24.733 --> 00:35:25.766
Take Judge Qin's statement.

00:35:26.566 --> 00:35:27.566
Inspector Tang.

00:35:30.633 --> 00:35:32.566
Historically, what has it taken...

00:35:32.833 --> 00:35:33.833
to right a wrong?

00:35:34.200 --> 00:35:35.200
Time.

00:35:37.100 --> 00:35:38.100
That means...

00:35:38.100 --> 00:35:39.233
what you see now...

00:35:40.400 --> 00:35:41.866
isn't the final result yet.

00:35:52.933 --> 00:35:53.933
When the prosecution...

00:35:53.933 --> 00:35:55.966
handed over the case to the judge,

00:35:55.966 --> 00:35:57.400
there was this list.

00:35:57.833 --> 00:35:59.033
When the arson case back then...

00:35:59.666 --> 00:36:00.966
came into my hands,

00:36:01.133 --> 00:36:02.366
after verification,

00:36:02.766 --> 00:36:04.433
I noticed that
a witness statement,

00:36:04.433 --> 00:36:06.600
labeled A05, was missing.

00:36:07.466 --> 00:36:09.066
So I asked them to resubmit it.

00:36:09.466 --> 00:36:10.466
Later on, this case...

00:36:10.766 --> 00:36:12.600
was handed over
to another prosecutor.

00:36:13.000 --> 00:36:14.566
I don't know if the statement...

00:36:15.200 --> 00:36:16.266
was resubmitted or not.

00:36:17.766 --> 00:36:19.033
Didn't you tell Shi Zhi Yang...

00:36:19.600 --> 00:36:20.866
that you didn't remember anything?

00:36:22.233 --> 00:36:23.600
Perhaps it's because I'm old now.

00:36:23.800 --> 00:36:25.200
My memory isn't very stable.

00:36:27.066 --> 00:36:28.066
What I want to ask is,

00:36:29.066 --> 00:36:30.800
why are you telling me this now?

00:36:32.466 --> 00:36:33.933
Consider it my way
of repaying you...

00:36:34.200 --> 00:36:35.600
for saving me in the parking lot.

00:36:47.600 --> 00:36:48.600
How did it go?

00:36:49.433 --> 00:36:50.433
It was the villagers...

00:36:50.433 --> 00:36:51.633
from the Old City District
who lost the lawsuit.

00:36:52.466 --> 00:36:53.566
We arrested the ringleaders.

00:36:54.000 --> 00:36:55.000
They'll be charged...

00:36:55.166 --> 00:36:56.400
with criminal damage
and attempted assault.

00:36:56.633 --> 00:36:57.733
Is Qin Yu all right?

00:36:58.233 --> 00:36:59.233
Do you know...

00:36:59.266 --> 00:37:01.833
that many eyes are on him now?

00:37:02.466 --> 00:37:03.933
We have to handle this quietly.

00:37:06.000 --> 00:37:07.000
Hey.

00:37:07.566 --> 00:37:08.566
Hello?

00:37:09.033 --> 00:37:10.133
I'm talking to you.

00:37:10.133 --> 00:37:11.166
Didn't you hear me?

00:37:15.166 --> 00:37:16.266
Qin Yu told me that...

00:37:16.833 --> 00:37:18.600
on the list of evidence
for the arson case,

00:37:18.933 --> 00:37:20.000
there was originally
a witness statement,

00:37:20.000 --> 00:37:21.800
labeled A05.

00:37:22.366 --> 00:37:23.466
But during the trial,

00:37:23.666 --> 00:37:25.333
this statement suddenly disappeared.

00:37:25.866 --> 00:37:27.466
I don't know
if it was an oversight...

00:37:27.833 --> 00:37:29.166
or if someone took it on purpose.

00:37:29.600 --> 00:37:30.866
If it was deemed useless...

00:37:31.066 --> 00:37:32.266
or unnecessary,

00:37:32.266 --> 00:37:33.366
they don't have to
submit it to court.

00:37:33.766 --> 00:37:34.766
It's normal.

00:37:35.033 --> 00:37:36.233
I don't know if it's normal or not.

00:37:36.833 --> 00:37:37.833
I just know...

00:37:37.833 --> 00:37:38.833
that at this stage,

00:37:38.833 --> 00:37:40.133
this A05 statement...

00:37:40.366 --> 00:37:41.666
is our only lead.

00:37:41.666 --> 00:37:42.666
Don't do it.

00:37:43.400 --> 00:37:44.833
If you open this file,

00:37:45.066 --> 00:37:46.766
Da Gama will surely know.

00:37:47.266 --> 00:37:49.233
Besides, you don't
even have access...

00:37:49.233 --> 00:37:50.766
to the headquarters' archives.

00:37:54.466 --> 00:37:56.766
Don't look at me like that.

00:38:02.633 --> 00:38:03.833
I won't help you.

00:38:04.466 --> 00:38:07.200
It might be 1977 or 1978.

00:38:07.400 --> 00:38:08.400
How about this?

00:38:08.400 --> 00:38:09.400
Can you show me...

00:38:09.766 --> 00:38:11.033
all the closed arson cases...

00:38:11.033 --> 00:38:12.033
from the past two years?

00:38:12.400 --> 00:38:15.133
I also want those that didn't go
to the initial trial.

00:38:15.400 --> 00:38:17.333
That means I want...

00:38:17.466 --> 00:38:19.366
all the most complete
statement records.

00:38:19.666 --> 00:38:21.133
That might be a lot of data.

00:38:21.466 --> 00:38:22.600
Not at all.

00:38:23.233 --> 00:38:25.833
Just find everything on my list.

00:38:25.833 --> 00:38:27.933
I just want to go through
the main points.

00:38:28.633 --> 00:38:30.000
I even brought my colleague...

00:38:30.000 --> 00:38:31.266
to help me out.

00:38:31.700 --> 00:38:32.700
I promise...

00:38:32.700 --> 00:38:34.833
I'll let you get off work
at 6pm sharp.

00:38:36.533 --> 00:38:38.000
Okay, Officer Hu,
please give me your permit...

00:38:38.000 --> 00:38:39.000
for registration.

00:38:39.133 --> 00:38:40.566
- This is the rule.
- Of course.

00:38:41.966 --> 00:38:42.966
Thank you for your help.

00:38:43.666 --> 00:38:46.933
Once I've looked at a file
and confirmed it,

00:38:46.933 --> 00:38:48.666
I'll tell you the file number.

00:38:48.666 --> 00:38:49.666
Okay.

00:39:24.166 --> 00:39:25.166
- Officer Hu.
- Yes.

00:39:25.166 --> 00:39:26.266
Have you figured out
which file you want to see?

00:39:26.833 --> 00:39:28.266
It's this one.

00:39:28.933 --> 00:39:29.933
Thank you so much.

00:39:30.033 --> 00:39:31.166
None of these three is it.

00:39:31.266 --> 00:39:32.266
I'll return them to you first.

00:39:32.966 --> 00:39:34.566
Okay. Then I'll register this one.

00:39:34.566 --> 00:39:35.566
Okay.

00:39:36.600 --> 00:39:37.866
You two take your time.

00:39:37.866 --> 00:39:39.033
I'll put the others back.

00:39:39.033 --> 00:39:40.033
Thank you, Madam.

00:39:40.533 --> 00:39:41.533
Hey, hurry up and read it!

00:39:41.533 --> 00:39:42.833
Don't keep the officer at work.

00:39:42.833 --> 00:39:43.833
We have to leave at six.

00:39:44.066 --> 00:39:45.066
Here.

00:39:59.066 --> 00:40:00.066
Did you find anything?

00:40:01.000 --> 00:40:02.000
This A05 statement...

00:40:02.000 --> 00:40:03.633
is an eyewitness statement.

00:40:04.266 --> 00:40:05.266
Although it's incomplete,

00:40:05.600 --> 00:40:07.433
but at least
two eyewitnesses claimed...

00:40:07.833 --> 00:40:10.333
that they saw a strange, tall man...

00:40:10.333 --> 00:40:11.833
at the scene.

00:40:12.166 --> 00:40:13.166
One of them also said...

00:40:13.266 --> 00:40:14.966
that the man was wearing a vest.

00:40:15.233 --> 00:40:16.666
He had a scar on his right shoulder,

00:40:17.000 --> 00:40:18.000
shaped like an earthworm.

00:40:18.366 --> 00:40:20.766
This man is the real arsonist?

00:40:22.433 --> 00:40:23.766
Who is this man?

00:40:24.766 --> 00:40:26.600
And who is protecting him?

00:41:07.700 --> 00:41:08.700
Chief Justice Qin.

00:41:08.700 --> 00:41:09.766
Someone from the Correctional
Services Department is here.

00:41:09.766 --> 00:41:10.766
They're here to pick up a document.